column1: I had so much fun celebrating Independence Day at the Alderson Parade today! Happy birthday to our great Nation! https://t.co/VxMxieFKiJ
Despite the rain I had a terrific day traveling to beautiful Monroe County and celebrating Farmer's Day with Chairman Duane Miller and members of the community! https://t.co/ojaB2IeSXc
Republican women need all the help we can get. I'm in Congress because of groups like @WinningForWomen and the vital role they play in electing more women.
